  \overline{x:A}  \\
  \vdots \\
  {B} 
  \end{array} } \\ {\begin{array}{c}
  \overline{s:\llbracket A  \rrbracket} \\
  \vdots \\
  \llbracket B \rrbracket  
    \end{array}}  }}}
    {\Box B}
\]%mdk
